If you want to insert the same runtime value at multiple locations, just give them the same name.
For example, {H0code|"\{person\}, \{person\}"|} will generate a {H0code|I18n -> String -> String|}
signature despite the fact that two placeholders have been specified and at runtime, calling the function with {H0code|Evan|} will
result in {H0code|Evan, Evan|}
